# ✅ Admin Panel – Digital Talent Management System  

## 💻 Desktop View  
The admin panel provides centralized control for managing users, roles, and system-wide settings.

### 🔹 Key Features  
- 👥 User Management: Add, edit, deactivate, or delete users  
- 🛡️ Role & Permissions: Assign roles and manage access levels  
- 📊 Dashboard Overview: View system metrics and activity  
- ⚙️ System Settings: Configure workflows and platform preferences  
- 📁 Data Management: Maintain organizational records  

### 👥 Role-Based Access  
- **HR Admin**: Full control over users, roles, and system settings  
- **Team Manager**: Limited access (view data, manage team-level info)  
- **Employee**: No direct access to admin panel  

- 🔔 Notifications: Alerts for system updates and user activities  

---

## 📱 Mobile View  
The mobile admin panel is optimized for quick monitoring and essential management tasks.

### 🔹 Key Features  
- ☰ Collapsible admin menu  
- 📊 Simplified dashboard  
- 👥 Quick user actions (activate/deactivate)  
- 🔔 Real-time system notifications  
- ⚡ Fast access to key controls  

---

## 🧠 Design Approach  
- Low-fidelity (Lo-Fi) wireframes  
- Focus on accessibility and control efficiency  
- Responsive design (Desktop + Mobile)  
- Minimal styling (grayscale, placeholders)  

